  "detailed_description": "Have you ever tried to understand musical notation? <br><br>With Arpsic, you can train yourself with intuitive lessons, learn the treble clef, bass clef, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.poster.avif?t=1724944267\" width=632 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.webm?t=1724944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.mp4?t=1724944267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With a straightforward interface, free piano, and experience points to help you in your music journey.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 clefs to practice music notation. <br></li><li>Free play mode with a midi piano full of weird sounds. <br></li><li>Get rewards and unlock new features. <br></li><li>1 song to learn, with more on the way. <br></li><li>1 piano voice. <br></li><li>Gain experience points and level up your skills. </li></ul><br>Coming soon!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>9 piano voices. <br></li><li>9 songs to learn<br></li><li>Practice your rhythm.</li></ul><br>Arpsic theme created by Komiku<br><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "Have you ever tried to understand musical notation? <br><br>With Arpsic, you can train yourself with intuitive lessons, learn the treble clef, bass clef, and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.poster.avif?t=1724944267\" width=632 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.webm?t=1724944267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713340/extras/7a242abf6af86eadfcaecbe554a5000f.mp4?t=1724944267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With a straightforward interface, free piano, and experience points to help you in your music journey.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 clefs to practice music notation. <br></li><li>Free play mode with a midi piano full of weird sounds. <br></li><li>Get rewards and unlock new features. <br></li><li>1 song to learn, with more on the way. <br></li><li>1 piano voice. <br></li><li>Gain experience points and level up your skills. </li></ul><br>Coming soon!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>9 piano voices. <br></li><li>9 songs to learn<br></li><li>Practice your rhythm.</li></ul><br>Arpsic theme created by Komiku<br><br><br>",
